(@p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, 1),

INSERT ([CreatedBy], [CreatedDt], [ImagePath], [IsDeleted], [IsPrimaryImage], [ModifiedBy], [ModifiedDt], [Name], [ProductId])
VALUES (i.[CreatedBy], i.[CreatedDt], i.[ImagePath], i.[IsDeleted], i.[IsPrimaryImage], i.[ModifiedBy], i.[ModifiedDt], i.[Name], i.[ProductId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;
